      "id": "s052b",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "现在做个诊断：如果两类中心位置不变，但每一类内部的点都被拉得更散，LDA 里哪个量会明显变大？"
      ],
      "type": "exercise"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "J(\\mathbf{w}) = \\frac{\\mathbf{w}^T S_B \\mathbf{w}}{\\mathbf{w}^T S_W \\mathbf{w}}",
        "spoken": "最大化这个比值，就是 LDA 的目标。"
      },
      "id": "s053",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "Fisher 准则可以写成矩阵形式："
      ],
      "type": "formula"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "generalized_eigenvalue_problem"
      ],
      "id": "s054",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "generalized_eigenvalue_problem"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "求解这个优化问题，会得到一个<term id=\"generalized_eigenvalue_problem\">广义特征值问题</term>：",
        "\\(S_B \\mathbf{w} = \\lambda S_W \\mathbf{w}\\)。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s055",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "对于二分类问题，解可以简化：",
        "\\(\\mathbf{w} = S_W^{-1}(\\boldsymbol{\\mu}_2 - \\boldsymbol{\\mu}_1)\\)。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
